      tq_v_4b V : at n_ctx=16384 (same tier as q4_0)
  - all successful runs: graph splits = 1
  - V-cache quantisation gives exactly one more context tier; not proportional
    to the V cache savings because K is still f16 (256 MiB at n_ctx=16384)
    and compute buffer is ~1014 MiB fixed
